                <p>For security and network management purposes, we may monitor network traffic. This includes logging connection times, data usage, device information, and websites visited. This data is used solely for network security and troubleshooting purposes.</p>

                <h2>4. Session Limits</h2>
                <p>Guest sessions are limited to <strong>24 hours</strong>. Bandwidth may be limited to ensure fair usage for all guests. You may reconnect after your session expires.</p>

                <h2>5. No Warranty</h2>
                <p>This network is provided <strong>"as is"</strong> without any warranty of any kind. We do not guarantee availability, speed, security, or reliability of the connection.</p>

