                <h2>7. Your Responsibility</h2>
                <p>You are responsible for maintaining the security of your own device. We recommend using a VPN and ensuring your device's firewall is enabled when using any public WiFi network.</p>

                <h2>8. Termination</h2>
                <p>We reserve the right to terminate your access to this network at any time without notice for any violation of these terms or for any other reason at our sole discretion.</p>

                <h2>9. Changes to Terms</h2>
                <p>We may modify these terms at any time without prior notice. Continued use of the network after any changes constitutes your acceptance of the new terms.</p>

